name: My Name is Panam by Alisa Speese

metadata.name: Serendipity
metadata.description: The first photo I made in Panamá and the foundation of all others. I heard tiny feet behind me and turned to see this small girl running towards me at full speed. I literally had to step out of her path as she chased her brother, who had taken her pink scooter. Her determination is contagious!
